<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brand OS — KRAFTT Movement · S4J4</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --c1: #F0EBE1;
    --c2: #C4845A;
    --c3: #4A3B2E;
    --c4: #FAF7F2;
    --c5: #2575FC;
    --font-heading: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --bg: var(--c3);
    --surface: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c3) 80%, var(--c2) 20%);
    --surface-2: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c3) 65%, var(--c2) 35%);
    --border: rgba(240,235,225,0.12);
    --border-mid: rgba(240,235,225,0.22);
    --text-primary: var(--c1);
    --text-muted: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c1) 55%, transparent);
    --text-accent: var(--c2);
    --radius: 8px;
    --radius-lg: 14px;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    min-height: 100vh;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 16px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ── LOCK SCREEN ── */
  #lock-screen {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999;
    background: var(--bg);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }
  #lock-screen.unlocking { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .lock-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .lock-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary); text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .lock-sub { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .pin-container { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .pin-digit {
    width: 48px; height: 58px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-mid);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: center; outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    caret-color: var(--text-accent);
  }
  .pin-digit:focus { border-color: var(--text-accent); }
  .pin-error { color: #e05252; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; height: 20px; }
  .lock-hint { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; }

  /* ── VAULT ── */
  #vault { display: none; min-height: 100vh; }
  #vault.visible { display: block; }

  /* ── TOPBAR ── */
  .topbar {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 88%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    height: 56px;
  }
  .topbar-brand { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .topbar-name { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-accent); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 92vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, color-mix(in srgb, var(--c5) 10%, transparent) 0%, transparent 70%);
    top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.2s forwards;
  }
  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.4s forwards;
  }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.6s forwards;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    display: flex; gap: 2rem; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0; animation: fade-up 0.8s 0.8s forwards;
  }
  .hero-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .hero-meta span::before { content: '·'; color: var(--text-accent); }

  /* ── MODULE NAV ── */
  .module-nav {
    position: sticky; top: 56px; z-index: 90;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 95%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 2rem; display: flex; gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .module-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .nav-item {
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted); padding: 14px 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap; text-decoration: none; display: block;
  }
  .nav-item:hover, .nav-item.active { color: var(--text-primary); border-bottom-color: var(--text-accent); }

  /* ── MODULES WRAPPER ── */
  .modules-wrapper { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem; }
  .module-section {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .module-section.in-view { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .module-label {
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .module-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); max-width: 80px; }
  .module-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* ── MODULE 1: MIRROR ── */
  .mirror-block {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--text-primary);
    position: relative;
  }
  .mirror-block::before {
    content: '\201C';
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 6rem; line-height: 0;
    color: var(--text-accent); opacity: 0.3;
    position: absolute; top: 2.5rem; left: 2rem;
  }
  .mirror-block p { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  .mirror-cite { color: var(--text-accent); font-style: italic; }

  /* ── MODULE 2: GOLDEN CIRCLE ── */
  .golden-circle { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .gc-item { background: var(--surface); padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  .gc-num { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .gc-heading { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 400; }
  .gc-text { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ── MODULE 3: FILTER ── */
  .filter-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .filter-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; }
  .filter-card.no { opacity: 0.8; }
  .filter-card-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .filter-card.yes .filter-card-label { color: var(--text-accent); }
  .filter-card.no .filter-card-label { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .filter-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ── MODULE 4: BRAND BOOK ── */
  .brand-book-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .bb-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; }
  .bb-card-title { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .color-swatches { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .swatch { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-mid); }
  .swatch-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .swatch-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .swatch-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .swatch-name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-primary); flex: 1; }
  .swatch-hex { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: monospace; }
  .swatch-rol { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); display: none; }
  .font-pair { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .font-demo-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .font-demo-sample-heading { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.2; }
  .font-demo-sample-body { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .sfeer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .sfeer-group-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sfeer-tags { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .sfeer-tag { font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; }
  .sfeer-tag.do { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c2) 15%, transparent); color: var(--c2); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c2) 25%, transparent); }
  .sfeer-tag.dont { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c4) 8%, transparent); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); text-decoration: line-through; }
  .sound-block { background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .typo-motivation { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0.75rem; }

  /* ── MODULE 5: TONE ── */
  .tone-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: hidden; }
  .tone-rule { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .tone-rule-num { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tone-rule span:last-child { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .tone-examples { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .tone-ex { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
  .tone-ex.wel { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .tone-ex-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tone-ex.wel .tone-ex-label { color: var(--text-accent); }
  .tone-ex.niet .tone-ex-label { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .tone-ex p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── MODULE 6: BLUEPRINT ── */
  .blueprint-intro { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .blueprint-intro-item { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }
  .bpi-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .bpi-value { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .sections-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-item { background: var(--surface); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .section-item:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .section-item-header { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .section-pos { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); padding-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 28px; }
  .section-content { flex: 1; }
  .section-name { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 400; }
  .section-headline { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .section-rol { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; display: none; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .section-item.open .section-rol { display: block; }
  .section-rol strong { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500; }
  .section-cta-chip { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 4px 12px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c5) 15%, transparent); color: var(--c5); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c5) 25%, transparent); border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; }

  /* ── MODULE 7: TAGLINES ── */
  .tagline-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .tagline-item { background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem 2rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.5rem; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .tagline-item:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .tagline-item.aanbevolen { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c2) 8%, var(--surface)); border-left: 3px solid var(--text-accent); }
  .tagline-num { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); padding-top: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 32px; }
  .tagline-body { flex: 1; }
  .tagline-text { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.35rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .tagline-why { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .tagline-badge { font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 10px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c2) 15%, transparent); color: var(--text-accent); border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; align-self: flex-start; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px; }
  .aanbeveling-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; }
  .aanbeveling-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-accent); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .aanbeveling-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .vault-footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 3rem 2rem; text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .vault-footer span { color: var(--text-accent); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fade-up { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .golden-circle { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .filter-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .brand-book-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tone-examples { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tone-ex.wel { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .blueprint-intro { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .pin-container { gap: 6px; }
    .pin-digit { width: 40px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LOCK SCREEN -->
<div id="lock-screen" role="main" aria-label="Access protection">
  <p class="lock-logo">S4J4 · Signal Architecture</p>
  <h1 class="lock-title">KRAFTT Movement<br>Brand OS Vault</h1>
  <p class="lock-sub">Enter your 6-digit access code</p>
  <div class="pin-container" id="pin-inputs">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 1">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 2">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 3">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 4">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 5">
    <input class="pin-digit" type="text" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="1" aria-label="Digit 6">
  </div>
  <p class="pin-error" id="pin-error" aria-live="polite">&nbsp;</p>
  <p class="lock-hint">Code received via email from S4J4</p>
</div>

<!-- VAULT -->
<div id="vault" aria-label="Brand OS Vault">

  <nav class="topbar" aria-label="Vault navigation">
    <span class="topbar-brand">S4J4 · Brand OS Vault</span>
    <span class="topbar-name">KRAFTT Movement</span>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero" aria-label="Intro">
    <p class="hero-label">Brand OS · 11 May 2026</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">KRAFTT Movement</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Sweat. Strengthen. Transform.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span>Clients</span>
      <span>English</span>
      <span>7 modules</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="module-nav" aria-label="Module navigation">
    <a href="#m1" class="nav-item">01 · Mirror</a>
    <a href="#m2" class="nav-item">02 · Core</a>
    <a href="#m3" class="nav-item">03 · Filter</a>
    <a href="#m4" class="nav-item">04 · Brand Book</a>
    <a href="#m5" class="nav-item">05 · Tone</a>
    <a href="#m6" class="nav-item">06 · Blueprint</a>
    <a href="#m7" class="nav-item">07 · Taglines</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="modules-wrapper">

    <!-- MODULE 1 -->
    <section id="m1" class="module-section">
      <p class="module-label">Module 01</p>
      <h2 class="module-title">Identity Mirror</h2>
      <div class="mirror-block">
        <p>You run a studio in Berlin where Pilates meets real strength training &mdash; not the rehabilitative kind, but serious work. In a room held at 45 degrees. People walk in and think: what have I done to myself. But after the session? They want to come back every week. You said it exactly right: <span class="mirror-cite">&ldquo;Het is zweten als ritueel, kracht als fundament, en het lichaam dat reageert op warmte op een manier die je nergens anders voelt.&rdquo;</span><br><br>You started as a Pilates instructor and felt something was always missing. Pilates was beautiful but not enough &mdash; you wanted to get stronger, not just more mobile. You wanted to build a space where people actually work, not pose. Berlin gave you permission: <span class="mirror-cite">&ldquo;Berlijn heeft dat rauwheid &mdash; mensen hier houden niet van bullshit. Ze willen iets dat werkt.&rdquo;</span><br><br>Your compass: <span class="mirror-cite">&ldquo;Je lichaam is sterker dan je denkt. En de enige manier om dat te weten, is het bewijs. Niet de theorie.&rdquo;</span><br><br>You&rsquo;ve also spotted a real gap in your own visual identity &mdash; the warmth of the heat promise sitting in tension with a cold accent color. That tension is honest. It can be made intentional. KRAFTT Movement is a studio for people who want an honest hour, not a lifestyle brand.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MODULE 2 -->
    <section id="m2" class="module-section">
      <p class="module-label">Module 02</p>
      <h2 class="module-title">Resonance Core</h2>
      <div class="golden-circle">
        <div class="gc-item">
          <p class="gc-num">WHY</p>
          <h3 class="gc-heading">Why</h3>
          <p class="gc-text">You built KRAFTT Movement because Pilates alone wasn&rsquo;t enough &mdash; and you saw that the doers, expats, and 30-somethings of Prenzlauer Berg needed the same thing: a place to actually work, with no soft promises attached.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gc-item">
          <p class="gc-num">HOW</p>
          <h3 class="gc-heading">How</h3>
          <p class="gc-text">The KRAFTT Method refuses the false choice between alignment and intensity. Heat is used as a deliberate tool &mdash; not a gimmick &mdash; and the science behind it gets explained to every client, whether it&rsquo;s their first session or their fiftieth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gc-item">
          <p class="gc-num">WHAT</p>
          <h3 class="gc-heading">What</h3>
          <p class="gc-text">A heated Pilates and strength studio at Greifswalder Str. 223, Prenzlauer Berg, Berlin &mdash; where the trial session does the selling.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
